title: Fujitsu ESPRIMO E9900 Intel® Core™ i5 i5-650 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 500 GB Intel® GMA HD Windows 7 Professional SFF PC Black
description:
Fujitsu ESPRIMO E9900 Intel® Core™ i5 i5-650 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 500 GB Intel® GMA HD Windows 7 Professional SFF PC Black


Your desktop without compromises The ESPRIMO E9900 can be positioned vertically or horizontally - the ideal choice for your desk. Equipped with the with the all new 2010 Intel® Core™ vPro processor family, this PCs, made of environmentally-conscious material, operate reliably and quietly. Furthermore, these devices equipped with high efficient power supplies (up to 89%) meet today's ENERGY STAR® 5.0 criteria and features the world’s first 0-Watt technology (optional). Why compromise between a good conscience and top-quality equipment when you can have both at the same time? SPECIAL FEATURES -The all new 2010 Intel® Core™ vPro Processor Family. -genuine Windows® 7 Professional. -Flexible desktop solution – less than 13 liters volume. -Green PC. -Halogen-free mainboard. -Latest Intel® Q75 chipset. -Up to 89 % energy efficient power supply. GREEN IT Fujitsu is committed to eliminating the use of harmful and potentially harmful substances in its products and production processes in order to minimize risk to end users and to the environment. This strategy is captured in Environmental Guideline FTS03230 and forms the basis on which all Fujitsu's products are designed. Especially for ESPRIMO PCs this means that all used printed circuit boards are halogen free. Furthermore they are compliant with several certificates awarding environmental conscience such as Blue Angel, Nordic Star, ENERGY STAR® and EPEAT. ENERGY EFFICIENCY As energy saving is one of the core components of Fujitsu’ approach to the environment, we permanently try to improve the energy efficiency of our products. The ESPRIMO E features latest technology regarding Intel® chipset and processor and optional an up to 89% energy efficient power supply. Furthermore it delivers enhanced power management settings and optional 0-Watt power consumption in off- / hibernating mode. THE ALL NEW INTEL TECHNOLOGY Equipped with the newest Intel technology, Fujitsu’s PCs offer intelligent performance and are easy to manage and configure. Intel’s Hyper-threading Technology allows each processor core to work on two tasks at the same time while Intel’s Turbo Boost Technology automatically speeds up the processor when the user’s workload requires extra performance. Sophisticated new management technology allows businesses to easily maintain even unresponsive computers with tools such as remote configuration, diagnosis, isolation, and repair. MANAGEABILITY Maximum system security and manageability are of critical importance to IT managers. With the Intel vPro Technology and the integrated Intel Active Management Technology (iAMT), Intel is seeking to improve these levels still further, in the deskbound and notebook sector. The ESPRIMO 9000 Series supports Intel® vPro™ technology – simple administration made easier. FLEXIBILITY Each business has unique, specific requirements to its IT infrastructure. You have the freedom of choice in getting systems which perfectly fit in your specific environment with hardware, software, add-on and lifecycle management.

title: Lenovo ThinkCentre M910 Tiny Intel® Core™ i5 i5-7500T 4 GB DDR4-SDRAM 256 GB SSD Windows 10 Pro Mini PC Black
description:
Lenovo ThinkCentre M910 Tiny Intel® Core™ i5 i5-7500T 4 GB DDR4-SDRAM 256 GB SSD Windows 10 Pro Mini PC Black


Tiny Footprint, Big Statement At 96% smaller than a traditional desktop tower, the M910 Tiny is extremely compact. This tiny desktop fits just about anywhere and can be positioned horizontally or vertically—mount it on a wall, behind a monitor, or even under a desk. You can even power digital signage with a PC that’s easy to hide from view. It delivers reliable, professional-level performance, while freeing up valuable desk-space. The Benefits of Modular Design With the ThinkCentre M910 Tiny, you can create your own modular all-in-one PC. Simply use the Tiny inside the back of the ThinkCentre Tiny-in-One (TIO) display. Keep costs down when choosing to upgrade the display and computing power separately, and get more use from your assets over time. See the Bigger Picture With up to three independent displays, or four displays in Mosaic Mode, M910 Tiny expands the limits of desktop computing to enable greater productivity. Ideal for financial and creative industries – and all your multimedia, multitasking needs. Bigger Isn’t Necessarily Better Don’t be deceived by its miniature frame, as the ThinkCentre M910 Tiny punches well above its weight. Equipped with a 7th generation Intel® Core™ processor and PCIe SSD storage, you can power up in a flash and load files even faster. Intensive tasks like multimedia creation, graphic design, and number-crunching are a walk in the park. Help Is Just a Keystroke Away With high-performance Intel® Core™ vPro™ processors, your IT team can remotely access your fleet of desktops. They can easily roll out software upgrades or fixes to all PCs on the network, saving on both management costs and desk-side visit time. Lifecycle Stability With Intel® Stable Image Platform Program (SIPP), your ThinkCentre M910 Tiny is guaranteed to have platform availability for at least 12 months. So you can manage your PC lifecycle and keep costs down. Built for Business—Tested for Your Lifestyle The ThinkCentre M910 Tiny is built to last in any environment. It carries the Think name, which means it’s tested against military-specification requirements, as well as 200 rigorous quality checks. From enduring arctic temperatures of -20 degrees C, to desert heat of 60 degrees C, this device can more than handle the bumps and bruises of life.

title: Lenovo ThinkCentre M75q AMD Ryzen™ 5 PRO 3400GE 8 GB DDR4-SDRAM 256 GB SSD Windows 10 Pro Mini PC Black
description:
Lenovo ThinkCentre M75q AMD Ryzen™ 5 PRO 3400GE 8 GB DDR4-SDRAM 256 GB SSD Windows 10 Pro Mini PC Black


Amazingly compact, astonishingly powerful Built for productivity, the incredibly powerful ThinkCentre M75q Tiny packs a lot into its compact 1L chassis. High-performance AMD Ryzen™ PRO processing with lightning-quick memory and storage, plus rich Radeon™ Vega graphics, enables any task to be tackled with ease. What’s more, it’s so small that it doesn’t have to live on a desk, freeing up much-needed space. A big win for clutter-free thinking. It’s what's inside that counts ThinkCentre M75q Tiny may be compact but it’s built for productivity and speed. Packed with seamless AMD Ryzen™ 5 Pro processing, advanced DDR4 memory, ultra-fast PCIe SSD storage with 3D NAND technology, and powerful Radeon™ Vega graphics, it’s ready to tackle any task. One well connected PC With the M75q Tiny, all the input/output bases are covered—from audio to USB and video. The roster of ports includes a DisplayPort™ and full-function USB Type-C for power, display, and data—enabling fast, easy connectivity to other devices. Because security counts To help minimize cyber security attacks, such as malware and phishing, every M75q Tiny comes with AMD GuardMI Technology. This dedicated on-chip security approach provides system-level protection against various cyber threats and helps to safeguard your sensitive data. Go ahead, reclaim your desk With the M75q Tiny, you also get back some much-needed desk-space. Just 1L in volume, this sleek desktop can be securely deployed almost anywhere—mounted on the wall, under a desk, or behind a monitor. A lean, mean, & green machine MIL-SPEC tested for durability and reliability, the M75q Tiny can be counted on to perform in the most extreme conditions. What’s more, its energy efficiency and green certifications, such as Energy® Star 7.0, will result in lower utility bills for your business. How do you keep an IT manager happy? With features like the Trusted Platform Module (TPM) and Smart USB Protection to encrypt and help safeguard data. In addition, the M75q Tiny comes with DASH Manageability and Smart Power On, delivering a more flexible way to manage client systems and remote devices.

title: HP Elite 7500 MT + LE2202x Intel® Core™ i3 i3-3220 2 GB DDR3-SDRAM 500 GB Windows 8 Pro Micro Tower PC Black
description:
HP Elite 7500 MT + LE2202x Intel® Core™ i3 i3-3220 2 GB DDR3-SDRAM 500 GB Windows 8 Pro Micro Tower PC Black


A small business PC designed for performance, style and xpandability with Beats Audio™. Features Windows 8 Pro or other operating systems available State-of-the art computing - Your small business computing needs can change at the click of a mouse. You need a PC that can keep up. The HP Elite 7500 is designed to give you the high performance you need for today’s process-intensive and graphics-rich applications and the sleek new design complements any home office or small business environment. Technology for today and tomorrow - Intel® Core™ i3, Core i5 or Core i7 3rd Generation processors provide top speeds and multiple cores for some of the most demanding applications you’ll ever need to run. Paired with the powerful Intel H67 Express Chipset, you get a PC that’s affordable and performance ready. Flexibility at your fingertips - Including four memory slots, PCI Express slots, internal and external drive bays, the HP Elite 7500 Microtower Business PC is designed for customization and expansion. - Data is what it is all about, and your files aren’t getting any smaller. USB 3.0 ports give you higher transfer rates than USB 2.0 in order to match the new usage and larger devices being developed. - The highly expandable HP Elite 7500 Microtower is intended to fit a wide range of space and configuration requirements. The sleek new design with its high-gloss finish and rounded corners is meant to be shown off. Out-of-the-box productivity - The HP Elite 7500 does all the heavy lifting with no matter how extensive a list of features you desire. Configuration options include a variety of optical drives and hard drives, and memory configurations up to 16GB. Dual hard drives can be structured in a RAID configuration to automatically back up and protect your stuff. And, with preinstalled software like the HP Power Assistant, you get a PC equipped to make an impact right out of the box. Give your business a boost - With Beats Audio™, HP has engineered an audio system that unlocks all of the sounds musicians and producers have perfected in the studio. You hear the highs, lows and subtle in-betweens like never before. - Plus, the HP Elite 7500 offers business class service and support so you can spend your time focusing on what’s most important—your business.
